<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7ab04f3b-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s9521"><num value="9521">§ 9521.</num><heading> Definition</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this part, the term “MBDA Business Center Program” means the program established under section ___113. <ref class="footnoteRef" idref="fn002663">1</ref><note type="footnote" id="fn002663"><num>1</num> So in original. See References in Text note below.</note></p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7ab04f3c-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/pl/117/58/dK/tI/s100111">Pub. L. 117–58, div. K, title I, § 100111</ref>, <date date="2021-11-15">Nov. 15, 2021</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/135/1451">135 Stat. 1451</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id7ab04f3d-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id7ab04f3e-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="id7ab04f3f-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section ___113, referred to in text, probably means <ref href="/us/pl/117/58/s100113">section 100113 of Pub. L. 117–58</ref>, which is classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t15/s9523">section 9523 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
